   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cc79c66d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Dynamic Pricing for Perishable Inventory — Pipeline Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook calls the modular pipeline (`config.py`, `data_loading.py`, `demand_forecast.py`, etc.) stage by stage so you can see intermediate results.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Before running:** activate the conda env (`conda activate dynamic_pricing`) and start Jupyter from the `code/` folder so the imports resolve.\n",
    "\n",
    "To run everything in one shot: `Cell` → `Run All`.\n",
    "\n",
    "To run one stage at a time: click into a cell and `Shift+Enter`.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "95fe6f76",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 0 · Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "Make sure the current working directory is `code/` so the modules can be imported."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "d014fb23",
   "metadata": {},
