      "Models will be written to : C:\\Users\\Bhavana\\Downloads\\Capstone_Missouri\\Capstone_Missouri\\models\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import config, data_loading, features, demand_forecast, elasticity, spoilage, optimizer, simulation, sensitivity\n",
    "\n",
    "config.ensure_dirs()\n",
    "print(\"All modules imported.\")\n",
    "print(\"Outputs will be written to:\", config.OUTPUTS_DIR)\n",
    "print(\"Models will be written to :\", config.MODELS_DIR)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8e2fcfd4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1 · Load perishable dataset & build the 3-way split\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Train** : everything before the last 90 days  \n",
    "- **Validation** : days -90 to -61 (used for model selection only)  \n",
    "- **Holdout** : last 60 days (sacred — not touched until Stage 4)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
