  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "88ab3cfc",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6 · Sensitivity analyses (Stage 5)\n",
    "\n",
    "Three checks:\n",
    "1. **High-spoilage subset** — re-run all 3 strategies on items with `days_until_expiry ≤ 3`.\n",
    "2. **Elasticity ±50%** — both on the full sample AND on non-near-expiry rows only (the one that actually tests whether the regular elasticity is doing work).\n",
    "3. **Optimizer stability** — discount distribution on a 1k-row pre-holdout sample."
   ]
  },
